# macOS Finder copy-and-paste duplicates ("foo 2.rs", "foo 2.swift" …).
# Cargo treats `*.rs` in `tests/` as a separate test target, and "foo 2"
# is not a valid crate name, so a stray copy will break `cargo test`.
* 2.rs
* 2.swift
* 2.toml
* 2.lock
* 2.md
* 2.png
* 2.icns

